NFS  L1.1.45 DX66 L1.1.45 DX33 12550N  152x     10   75818   70916  A
sun  S4.1.3   SS2                               30  921751  633226  A
NFS  S4.1.3   SS2  S4.1.3                       20  115225  758127  A
irix I5.2     r4k                               30 2147254 1155243  A

Key:

