        L1.0.9  - Linux version 1.0.9
        S4.1.3  - SunOS version 4.1.3
        I5.2    - Irix version 5.2

 CPU:
        DX33 - I486DX/33
        DX66 - I486DX2/66
        SS2 - SparcStation 2
        r4k - R4000 (100 MHz?)

