        12550N - Seagate 12500N
        12400N - Seagate 12400N
        31200N - Seagate 31200N

 Adapter:
        152x - Adaptec 1520/1522
        154x - Adaptec 1540/1542

 Meg: Number of megabytes iozone wrote and read

